The question on everyone’s mind has been answered. Www.mobserver.co.za paid a visit to Middelburg’s most loved speed walker Disco on Tuesday. Sipho Mashiana affectionally known as Disco told www.mobserver.co.za that the reason residents do not see him power walk from Mhluzi to the CBD is because he has found a new route on the N4. Enjoy a video of Disco demonstrating his speed-walking abilities. Read more in this week’s edition of the Middelburg Observer. 